articles.title: GE to end its run as a conglomerate, split into 3 companies - CP24 Toronto's Breaking News
articles.description: General Electric, the storied American manufacturer that struggled under its own weight after growing to become a sprawling conglomerate, will divide itself into three public companies focused on aviation, health care and energy.
